episodes.title: The Auguries
episodes.plot: Seven years after the demise of Rehoboam, events are set in motion that reunite allies and enemies.

episodes.title: Well Enough Alone
episodes.plot: Maeve and Caleb search for answers. Christina investigates Peter Myers. William announces a new Delos venture.

episodes.title: Années Folles
episodes.plot: Bernard begins his journey. Maeve finds herself in familiar territory. Caleb sees someone he loves.

episodes.title: Generation Loss
episodes.plot: Maeve and Caleb attempt to escape Temperance with their lives. Bernard and the resistance search for a weapon in the desert.

episodes.title: Zhuangzi
episodes.plot: Christina questions the nature of her reality. Charlotte tasks William with tracking a human outlier who has breached.

episodes.title: Fidelity
episodes.plot: Caleb attempts to escape from Charlotte's brutal interrogation, and uncovers a disturbing reality. Bernard and C make their way to the resistance hideout, only to find a spy in their midst.

episodes.title: Metanoia
episodes.plot: Bernard and Maeve fight to save the world. Charlotte begins to see her plans realized. The Man in Black returns to the game.

episodes.title: Que Será, Será
episodes.plot: Christina finds the center of the maze; Caleb and C try to escape; William changes the game's difficulty, to Hale's furious disapproval.
